nodes.text: A Nautolan female Force-user lived during the Galactic Civil War.

She was a practitioner of the second form of lightsaber combat, known as Makashi, and wielded a red-bladed lightsaber. She was a follower of the dark side of the Force and at some point during the galaxy-wide conflict, she dueled Jedi archaeologist Rachi Sitra.
The Nautolan was adept at conjuring Force lightning.
